          "type": "npc_line",
          "speakerId": "NARRATOR",
          "text": "There are multiple numbers. Each promises authority. (pause)\nNone promises help. (pause)\n\nNo one answers \u201cWho owns this corridor?\u201d out loud. (pause)\nPick a number: Compliance Desk, Safety Coordinator, or Facilities Operator.",
