        {
          "id": "N_COMMIT_WRITEUP",
          "type": "npc_line",
          "speakerId": "NARRATOR",
          "text": "You write it in the only language that survives audits. (pause)\n\n- Training-date interlock blocks enable or access. (pause)\n- LOTO prevents manipulation without your lock and a verified zero-energy state. (pause)\n- Ventilation must be NORMAL before access or verification. (pause)\n- The interlock inhibits the indicator. (pause)\n\nYour handwriting stays steady. (pause)\nYour jaw doesn\u2019t. That counts as composure.",
